{"type": "article", "id": 29715, "title": "灵感来源于法压壶的台灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-18T11:55:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 64, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160717201839NBnapZyuRzeThOSY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>忘掉那些传统的调光器吧，掌握明暗有更有趣的方式：来自伦敦的 Menashri 夫妇借鉴了注射器的原理设计了这款像是法压壶的台灯 <a href=\"http://www.getdimo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">DiMO</a>。</p>\n<p>这个造型简洁的灯具需要人们通过推拉来控制开关和灯光强度，Menashri 夫妇还额外设计了一款带旋钮设计的 Plus 版本。为了更好地配合“液体灯光”的概念，塑料灯罩的上下两端都搭配了山毛榉木制成的组件，带给人一种温暖的居家感受。</p>\n<p>你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1505908341/dimo-lamp-control-your-light\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，两种款式的最低价分别为 55 和 75 英镑。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607172038550Hj6hF3gobBNa48Y.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160717203852wjhfdr6e5zBGykSt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160717203852qPRgHeKYMTmkJQhV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160717203927iv5d80DLJpbuTl2c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n"}